item.description: In this jam-packed Master Class you’ll learn why apathy may be the reason you’re feeling burned out in dating and how empathy is the antidote. Damona shares why empathy makes you more attractive, how to cultivate it, and exercises to strengthen both self-empathy and relational empathy... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/datesandmates

item.title: #60 From Stuck to Unstoppable with Todd Jason
item.description:
Most men wake up every day without a clear vision for their future. They’re grinding, they’re hustling, but deep down, they don’t know if they’re actually building the life they want.

If you feel stuck, like you're coasting through life without real direction, this conversation will change the way you think about your future.

I sit down with Todd Jason to break down why clarity is the foundation of success, fulfillment, and freedom - and how you can develop it... Feed: https://app.kajabi.com/podcasts/2147497360/feed
